overview: Do you know the muffin girls? They're young and ready to fuck. For over 2 hours and twenty minutes, you can watch these young fluffy muffins get stuffed like a raw turkey on Thanksgiving day. Lindsey Meadows and Ginger Lee get hog-shemped and Manuel Ferrara strains his main vein. And Sativa Rose experiences a new type of confession with Mark Ashley in the temple of his first holy monkey. It's a flippin' fabulous time, because there's nothing better than whippin' out your flesh-eating flogenstein to stuff some young muffins!
title: Stuffin' Young Muffins 5
